{"shared_messages": [{"role": "user", "visible": "Solve the following math problem step by step. The last line of your response should be of the form \"ANSWER: $ANSWER\" (without quotes) where $ANSWER is the answer to the problem.\n\nDistinct points $A$ and $B$ are on a semicircle with diameter $MN$ and center $C$.  The point $P$ is on $CN$ and $\\angle CAP = \\angle CBP = 10^\\circ$.  If arc $MA$ is equal to $40^\\circ$, then find arc $BN$ (in degrees).\n\n[asy]\nimport geometry;\nimport graph;\n\nunitsize(2 cm);\n\npair A, B, C, M, N, P;\n\nM = (-1,0);\nN = (1,0);\nC = (0,0);\nA = dir(140);\nB = dir(20);\nP = extension(A, A + rotate(10)*(C - A), B, B + rotate(10)*(C - B));\n\ndraw(M--N);\ndraw(arc(C,1,0,180));\ndraw(A--C--B);\ndraw(A--P--B);\n\nlabel(\"$A$\", A, NW);\nlabel(\"$B$\", B, NE);\nlabel(\"$C$\", C, S);\nlabel(\"$M$\", M, SW);\nlabel(\"$N$\", N, SE);\nlabel(\"$P$\", P, S);\n[/asy]\n\nRemember to put your answer on its own line at the end in the form \"ANSWER: $ANSWER\" (without quotes) where $ANSWER is the answer to the problem, and you do not need to use a \\boxed command.", "reasoning": null}], "samples": [{"id": "math_060db1e8", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_12208a28", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_12353c85", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_14642e49", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_1584ff1d", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_263aae24", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_2d327aa9", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_2ddfe2f8", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_2f98bcfe", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_31fd238b", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_36a96426", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_394b9fb6", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "messages": []}, {"id": "math_3d37bdfa", "epoch": 1, "scores": {}, "message